							<h3>4th ZRCP Joint Annual Conference</h3>
							<p>
								Delivered invited talk at <strong>4th ZRCP Joint Annual Conference, Hotel Verde, Zanzibar</strong> on
								"How can Innovation Modernize the Public Service Delivery and Create Inclusive Digital Economy"
								on 27th August 2025.
							</p>
							<div class="achievement-tags">
								<span class="achievement-tag workshop">Invited Talk</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag africa">Africa</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
						<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<div class="timeline-date">August 2025</div>
							<h3>Best Poster Award at Deep Learning Indaba</h3>
							<p>
								Won the Best Poster Award in the Publication & Dataset Category at
								Deep Learning Indaba 2025 in Kigali, Rwanda (16-23 August 2025), for presenting the CARA-FMs Framework
								for Context-Aware and Responsible AI in East Africa. Also presented oral talk at the Responsible AI Workshop
								on 21st August 2025.
							</p>
							<div class="achievement-tags">
								<span class="achievement-tag award">Award Winner</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag conference">International</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag africa">Africa</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

