							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
						<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<div class="timeline-date">February 2025</div>
							<h3>UNESCO AI Readiness Consultation</h3>
							<p>
								Participated in <strong>National Stakeholders Consultations for Tanzania on the UNESCO Readiness Assessment
								Methodology (RAM) on Artificial Intelligence</strong> at Madinat Al Bahr Hotel, Zanzibar on Thursday, 20 February 2025,
								contributing to national-level AI policy and strategy development.
							</p>
							<div class="achievement-tags">
								<span class="achievement-tag policy">Policy Impact</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag international">International</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag africa">Africa</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
						<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<div class="timeline-date">2024-2025</div>
							<h3>Lab Establishment & Growth</h3>
							<p>
								Successfully established SAAIL Lab at IIT Madras Zanzibar, recruited talented
								MTech students, and initiated multiple research projects in agriculture AI,
								healthcare imaging, and assistive technologies.
							</p>
							<div class="achievement-tags">
								<span class="achievement-tag milestone">Milestone</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag team">Team Building</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item" data-aos="fade-up">
						<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<div class="timeline-date">2024-2026</div>
							<h3>Strategic Partnerships</h3>
							<p>
								Established collaborations with RuTAG IIT Madras Chennai for agricultural data
								ecosystems, Penn State University for medical imaging research, and Cadre
								Technologies for assistive technology development.
							</p>
							<div class="achievement-tags">
								<span class="achievement-tag collaboration">Partnership</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag international">International</span>
