						<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<div class="timeline-date">Ongoing</div>
							<h3>Research Impact Metrics</h3>
							<p>
								Growing research portfolio with <strong>25 publications, 994 citations</strong>
								(h-index: 14, i10-index: 15), and multiple ongoing projects addressing real-world
								challenges in East Africa through AI innovation and ethical technology development.
							</p>
							<div class="achievement-tags">
								<span class="achievement-tag metrics">Impact</span>
								<span class="achievement-tag research">Research</span>
							</div>
