			<div class="container">
				<div class="reflection-card">
					<h2>Looking Forward</h2>
					<div class="reflection-content">
						<p>
							2025 has been a year of remarkable growth and recognition for SAAIL Lab. From winning
							the Best Poster Award at Deep Learning Indaba to consulting with UNESCO on AI policy,
							we have demonstrated the power of ethical, context-aware AI research that bridges
							cutting-edge innovation with practical impact.
						</p>
						<p>
							Our work continues to address the unique challenges faced by East African communities‚Äîwhether
							improving agricultural productivity through precision farming, advancing healthcare diagnostics,
							or creating assistive technologies for accessibility. Every project reflects our commitment
							to responsible innovation and community engagement.
						</p>
						<p>
							We thank all members of the lab and our partners for a year of impactful research. We look
							forward to scaling our efforts in 2026!
						</p>
						<div class="reflection-signature">
							<p><strong>Dr. Innocent Nyalala</strong></p>
							<p>Founding Principal Investigator, SAAIL Lab</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<ModernFooter />
</Layout>

